record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 106
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H. RES. 106 -- (House of Representatives - October 02, 2007)

[Page: H11129]

speaking.paragraph: Madam Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to have my name removed as a cosponsor of H. Res. 106.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Missouri?
